CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784751302
OL,3,CPotential for prescription charges as
OL,4,Cwasted medicines cost #500,000 each
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FWasted medicines are costing Jersey's
OL,8,FHealth and Care Department half a
OL,9,Fmillion pounds each year, according to
OL,10,Frecent government data.
OL,12,FIslanders are being asked to manage
OL,13,Ftheir prescriptions more carefully -
OL,14,Fwith Health Care Jersey saying waste
OL,15,Fremains a "significant issue" with big
OL,16,Fcost, resource, and environmental
OL,17,Fimplications.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784751302
OL,3,CPotential for prescription charges as
OL,4,Cwasted medicines cost #500,000 each
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FThe campaign has been launched as the
OL,8,Fisland's Health Minister, Senator Tom
OL,9,FBinet, told the Jersey Evening Post
OL,10,Fthat islanders may have to start
OL,11,Fpaying for prescriptions to help meet
OL,12,Frising costs.
OL,14,FWhilst prescriptions have been free in
OL,15,FJersey since 2008, Senator Binet said
OL,16,Fhe "did not believe the policy was
OL,17,Fever a wise one".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784751302
OL,3,CPotential for prescription charges as
OL,4,Cwasted medicines cost #500,000 each
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FThe island's free prescriptions scheme
OL,8,Fcosts over 25 million pounds per year
OL,9,Fto run - but with #500,000 of that
OL,10,Flost on unused medicines, the possible
OL,11,Fintroduction of prescription charges
OL,12,Fcould be a way to tackle the waste
OL,13,Fproblem.
OL,15,FAcross the UK, almost 10% of all
OL,16,Fdispensed medicines are ultimately
OL,17,Fwasted.
OL,19,FHowever, prescriptions are not free
OL,20,Feverywhere.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784751302
OL,3,CPotential for prescription charges as
OL,4,Cwasted medicines cost #500,000 each
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FWhilst Wales, Northern Ireland, and
OL,8,FScotland run free prescriptions
OL,9,Fschemes similar to Jersey's, in
OL,10,FEngland they cost #9.90.
OL,12,FIn Guernsey, patients are charged
OL,13,F#5.40 per prescription, and in the
OL,14,FIsle of Man they cost #3.85.
OL,16,FJersey pharmacist Stephen Orme says
OL,17,Fthe question of charging for
OL,18,Fprescriptions is a "difficult" one,
OL,19,Fand any kind of charge would have to
OL,20,Fbe introduced with great caution.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784751302
OL,3,CPotential for prescription charges as
OL,4,Cwasted medicines cost #500,000 each
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FHe told ITV News there are rising
OL,8,Fcosts to consider - with pharmacies
OL,9,Fcurrently paid a fee of #3.96 by the
OL,10,Fgovernment to dispense medications,
OL,11,Fwhich they must use to cover all
OL,12,Foverhead costs including staff, rent,
OL,13,Fand electricity.
OL,15,FHowever, he adds: "I feel if you've
OL,16,Fgot an illness, it's not something
OL,17,Fthat you choose to have - it's not a
OL,18,Fluxury that should be taxed".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784751302
OL,3,CPotential for prescription charges as
OL,4,Cwasted medicines cost #500,000 each
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FStephen says when he worked in England
OL,8,Fhe felt the cost of dispensing
OL,9,Fprescriptions acted as a "deterrent"
OL,10,Ffor patients, with some "unable to
OL,11,Fafford to pay for all the items".
OL,13,FITV News has contacted Health Care
OL,14,FJersey to better understand what a
OL,15,Fpotential paid-for prescriptions
OL,16,Fscheme might look like, and is waiting
OL,17,Ffor a response.
OL,19,FMeanwhile, Health Care Jersey are
OL,20,Fasking islanders to help reduce waste
OL,21,Fby:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
